00074 void DataSetHeaderTest::NameValPairTest()
00075 {
00076         std::wstring p[] = {L"Uma",L"Thurman",L"Angelina",L"Jolie",L"Isabella ",L"Rossellini"};
00077         ParameterNameValueType t1;
00078         t1.SetName(p[0]);
00079         t1.SetValueText(p[1]);
00080         header->AddNameValParam(t1);
00081 
00082         ParameterNameValueType t2;
00083         t2.SetName(p[2]);
00084         t2.SetValueText(p[3]);
00085         header->AddNameValParam(t2);
00086 
00087         ParameterNameValueType t3;
00088         t3.SetName(p[4]);
00089         t3.SetValueText(p[5]);
00090         header->AddNameValParam(t3);
00091         ParameterNameValueTypeConstIt begin;
00092         ParameterNameValueTypeConstIt end;
00093         header->GetNameValIterators(begin, end);
00094         if(begin != end)
00095         {
00096                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(begin->GetName() == p[0]);
00097                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(begin->GetValueText() == p[1]);
00098                 begin++;
00099         }
00100         if(begin != end)
00101         {
00102                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(begin->GetName() == p[2]);
00103                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(begin->GetValueText() == p[3]);
00104                 begin++;
00105         }
00106         if(begin != end)
00107         {
00108                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(begin->GetName() == p[4]);
00109                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(begin->GetValueText() == p[5]);
00110         }
00111 }

00150 void DataSetHeaderTest::AssignmentTest()
00151 {
00152         header->SetName(L"pixel data");
00153         header->AddUShortColumn(L"Intensity");
00154         header->SetRowCnt(101);
00155         ParameterNameValueType t1;
00156         t1.SetName(L"Scanner");
00157         t1.SetValueText(L"M10");
00158         header->AddNameValParam(t1);
00159         ParameterNameValueType t2;
00160         t2.SetName(L"Pixel Size");
00161         t2.SetValueText(L"0.051");
00162         header->AddNameValParam(t2);
00163 
00164         DataSetHeader assignee;
00165         assignee = *header;
00166 
00167         // Check that the assignment worked
00168         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(assignee.GetName() == header->GetName());
00169         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(assignee.GetColumnCnt() == header->GetColumnCnt());
00170         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(assignee.GetNameValParamCnt() == header->GetNameValParamCnt());
00171         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(assignee.GetRowCnt() == header->GetRowCnt());
00172         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(assignee.GetColumnInfo(0) == header->GetColumnInfo(0));
00173 
00174         ParameterNameValueTypeConstIt nvpAssigneeBegin, nvpAssigneeEnd;
00175         assignee.GetNameValIterators(nvpAssigneeBegin, nvpAssigneeEnd);
00176         ParameterNameValueTypeConstIt nvpHeaderBegin, nvpHeaderEnd;
00177         assignee.GetNameValIterators(nvpHeaderBegin, nvpHeaderEnd);
00178         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(*nvpAssigneeBegin == *nvpHeaderBegin);
00179         ++nvpAssigneeBegin;
00180         ++nvpHeaderBegin;
00181         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(*nvpAssigneeBegin == *nvpHeaderBegin);
00182         ++nvpAssigneeBegin;
00183         ++nvpHeaderBegin;
00184         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpAssigneeBegin == nvpAssigneeEnd);
00185         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpHeaderBegin == nvpHeaderEnd);
00186 
00187         // TBD: no test of row offset array.
00188 }
